      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STOP IT ZIPPER (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (23.30) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including 10 wins. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can bounce back. HOOKED ON HOPE (1) finds it hard to win. Finished in the minors latest when third (22.66) at Gosford and may be close to breaking through. Solid record here winning three races. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to be in this for a long way. FASCINATE ABBY (8) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing seventh (23.39) at this track in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can feature with the right run.",
